{"tid":2414061,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"中大學生街上遭警察截停 其後將其拘捕帶回國安處處理","createTime":"2021-02-19T06:43:24.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-20T15:57:25.000Z","uid":225931,"like":3,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1ef732de9da190ab66a84e8db1774b7d6f13c226","tid":2414061,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T06:43:24.000Z","msg":"據香港電台網，一名中大學生涉嫌違反港版國安法及非法集結，被警方拘捕，被捕人士涉及去年11月19日在中大校園內遊行。<br />\n<br />\n消息指出，一名就讀中大哲學系學生因涉嫌觸犯「未經批准集結」及「煽動分裂國家罪」，今早（18日）於沙田區被警方拘捕。據悉，該學生涉於去年11月19日參與香港中文大學的校內遊行，並曾高喊口號及舉鼓吹「港獨」標語。<br />\n<br />\n消息續指，該名中大學生今日在街上遭香港警察截停搜查，其後將其拘捕，並帶返沙田警署扣留調查，案件已交由香港國安處處理。"},{"pid":"14b872e58bd5de193c8975c483cd4967a5fa54cf","tid":2414061,"uid":225931,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T06:44:02.000Z","msg":"著左中大Tee<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b27d9857ec4668bbea8c11f1e8567ba54b205313","tid":2414061,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T07:06:46.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35bea884d9562bb62b67ade4d2b8d49cea8693b5","tid":2414061,"uid":249960,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T07:08:32.000Z","msg":"吓？周圍拉件讀中大就當有份？"},{"pid":"49f77f09395799b7939ab506dee2b2091cde42d3","tid":2414061,"uid":225931,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"35bea884d9562bb62b67ade4d2b8d49cea8693b5","tid":2414061,"uid":249960,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T07:08:32.000Z","msg":"吓？周圍拉件讀中大就當有份？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T07:10:33.000Z","msg":"著左中大Tee掛 拉完再審"},{"pid":"4148711b60e19d483f0a4542a48f00dc32f505a8","tid":2414061,"uid":323876,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T07:11:38.000Z","msg":"第一次知原來響學校遊行要申請<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da777919953973509aeb728f8